author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Dixy Yug Acquires 23.67% Dixy Shares
text:
May 14 (Reuters) - Dixy:
* SAID ON FRIDAY DIXY YUG INCREASED ITS STAKE IN COMPANY TO 47.23 PCT FROM 23.56 PCT
* IN FEBRUARY DIXY RECEIVED MANDATORY TENDER OFFER FROM DIXY YUG
